Coffee Website ☕
🔹 Project Description

Coffee Website ek modern aur responsive coffee shop website hai jo HTML aur CSS ka use karke banayi gayi hai.
Is project me coffee products, milkshakes, blogs aur stylish UI design create kiya gaya hai.

Website ko mobile se lekar desktop tak responsive banaya gaya hai taaki har device me properly work kare.

🔹 What is Included in This Project
Responsive Navbar
Hero / Background Section
Top Coffee Categories
Milkshake Product Cards
Latest Blogs Section
Footer Section
Hover Effects
Responsive Design

🔹 How This Project is Made
HTML se website ka structure create kiya gaya hai
CSS Flexbox ka use karke layout design kiya gaya hai
CSS Hover Effects aur Transitions use kiye gaye hain
Responsive website banane ke liye Media Queries use ki gayi hain
Modern UI design aur spacing ka use karke clean layout create kiya gaya hai

🔹 Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Flexbox
Media Queries

🔹 Main Features
Fully Responsive Website
Modern Coffee Shop UI
Smooth Hover Effects
Product Cards Design
Blog Section
Attractive Footer Design

